review.reviewBody: Ordered a 12" everything special w/ no mushrooms, added salami. tasted good,  delivered hot, followed my requests. thank you, happy customer
this is not indian style pizza btw, dont get fooled by the ginger and cilantro. not bad pizza - its decent, 5/10 if you're looking for that indian style punjabi pizza but 7/10 otherwise.
My Favorite spot ever since I discovered it.  Best Pizza!
Supreme with extra cheese from here is my new favorite pizza!
Solid pie. Loads of toppings on the Supreme. One of the best pizza's I've had in Vancouver. My only criticism is the sauce was a bit bland, could use some more flavour.
